The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
河北医科大学第二医院麻醉科ICU护士 朱君宇澎湃新闻记者 吕新文2月21日，第八批河北省援鄂医疗队 175人又踏上了征程，至此，河北省共派出了1036名医护人员驰援湖北。
Zhu Junyu, a nurse in the Department of Anaesthesiology at Hebei Medical University No.2 Hospital, Lu Xinwen, a journalist and 175-member Hubei Medical Team from Hebei Province, sent 1,036 medical personnel to help Hubei province on February 21.
新冠肺炎的爆发，让我们度过了一个百感交集的春节，二十多天以来，普通民众的心情跟着疫情一起起起落落，最近终于看到了疫情的好消息——出院人数超过了确诊人数。
The outbreak of New Crown Pneumonia has given us a mixed feeling of the Spring Festival. For more than two decades, ordinary people have followed the epidemic's ups and downs, and recently witnessed the good news that the number of discharges has exceeded the number of people diagnosed.
在大家都觉得松了一口气的时候，还有无数医护人员为了最后的胜利默默坚守着，特别是重症病房的医护人员，他们不敢松劲，像他们职业生涯中的每一刻、每一天一样，但又有一些不一样，因为他们知道，现在他们守护的是一个个宝贵的生命，是一个个家庭的未来，更是全国人民的安全感。
As everyone breathed a sigh of relief, countless paramedics clung to the final victory, especially the intensive care staff, who dared not relent, as they did every moment and every day of their careers, knowing that now they were watching over precious lives, the future of families, and the sense of security of the nation.
这群医护人员中就有河北医科大学第二医院麻醉科的刘烨星，他去武汉已经二十多天了，一直坚守在武汉市第七医院的重症监护室。
Liu Yexing of the Anaesthesiology Department of Hebei Medical University No. 2 Hospital was among the group of medical workers. He had been in Wuhan for more than 20 days and had been holding the intensive care unit of Wuhan Seventh Hospital.
受访者供图刘烨星是在1月26日下夜班后紧急被征调出征武汉的，面对各种不确定性，他说他的心里也会慌，但是他又说：“人嘛，总要有些情怀与信仰。
In the face of all kinds of uncertainty, Liu Yexing, the interviewee who was urgently summoned to Wuhan after the night shift on January 26, said his mind panicked. But he added: "As for people, there must always be some feelings and beliefs
”到了武汉，面对防护物资的缺乏、医疗环境的复杂，任务的艰巨，他首先表达的是他看到了武汉同事的“无畏、勇敢、友善”和对河北同事的照顾。
When he arrived in Wuhan, faced with the shortage of protective materials, the complexity of the medical environment and the difficulty of the task, he first expressed his admiration for his Wuhan colleague's "fearlessness, courage and kindness" and his care for his Hebei colleagues.
武汉的重症监护病房，因为不能开空调，用医护人员的描绘是“冰火两重天”。
Wuhan's intensive care unit, because the air-conditioning can not be turned on, the use of medical staff is described as "two days of ice fire."
由于穿着封闭的防护服，口罩戴得紧密，重症病人因为治疗的需要，都是俯卧位，需要经常搬动病人，每次用力地操作后，医护人员就有缺氧窒息的感觉。
As a result of wearing a closed protective clothing, mask tight, patients with severe illness because of the need for treatment, they are prone position, often need to move patients, every hard operation, the medical staff will have a sense of hypoxia asphyxia.
常常是搬动病人后一身大汗，被凉风一吹又是满身冰冷，总是担心会感冒。
Often moved the patient after a big sweat, a cool breeze blowing is covered with cold, always worried about catching a cold.
为了节省防护服，工作六个小时不能吃东西、不能喝水，加上工作强度很大，常常饿到没知觉。
In order to save on protective clothing, six hours of work without food or water, coupled with the intensity of the work, are often so hungry that they are unconscious.
一开始会低血糖，为了防止低血糖的发生，他们上班之前需要克服饮食口味的不适应，哪怕太辣的菜难以下口，只吃白米饭，也要努力多吃再多吃。
In order to prevent hypoglycemia in the first place, they need to overcome the taste of food before work, even if too spicy dishes difficult to eat, only eat white rice, but also try to eat more and more.
所有这些痛苦，都要靠意志力去克服。
All these sufferings must be overcome by willpower.
尽管这样，烨星说：重症病人症状改善拔除气管导管后，由于插管时用的镇静药需要一段时间代谢，病人会出现谵妄状态，烨星说这时候的病人极端躁狂，会问候医护人员的“祖宗八代”、会把自己的留置针拔掉，甚至会去撕扯医护人员的口罩、防护服，一方面会伤害病人自己，也会给医护人员造成职业暴露的风险。
Despite this, Ye Xing said: severe patients symptoms improved extraction trachea catheter, because intubation used sedatives need a period of time metabolism, patients will delirium, Akiko said that the patients will be extremely manic, will greet the "eight generations of medical personnel," will pull their lien needles, will even tear medical personnel's masks, protective clothing, will harm themselves, will cause occupational exposure to health care personnel.
护理这样的病人风险很多。
Caring for a patient like this is risky.
但是烨星认为，“病人太可怜了，我一定要把最好的状态给他们，努力帮他们”。
But Ye Xing thinks, "the patient is too pathetic, I must give them the best state, try to help them."
尽管付出了许多，尽管承担了普通人无法想象也很难承担的责任，尽管每天靠意志力在坚持，烁烨星却觉得自己不是英雄，他说：在这个没有硝烟的战场上，在离生死最近的前沿阵地上，有多少刘烨星这样的白衣战士在“安静地优秀，悄无声息地坚强”，他们的愿望也许和烁烨星一样：“等疫情过后想和家人一起出去旅游，呼吸一下没有口罩的空气”。
In spite of all these efforts and responsibilities beyond the imagination of ordinary people and despite persistent willpower every day, Shaoyang feels like a non-hero. In this battlefield without smoke, on the front line of life and death, Liu Yexing and his white-clad soldiers may have the same desire to travel with their families and breathe the air without a mask.
无数个烨星是平凡的，也是不平凡的，最是平凡也感人！本期编辑邢潭推荐阅读。
Countless Ye star is ordinary, is also extraordinary, the most ordinary also touching! This issue editor Xingtan recommended reading.
